               stealing a cotton petticoat, value 20 s. a silk bonnet, value 2 s. a japan bread basket, value 1 s. a linen window curtain, value 6 d. a mahogany frame with three drawers, value 4 s. and a pair of paste ear-rings, value 10 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
