                     <interp inst="t17810222-30-person333" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I pursued the prisoner and saw him taken.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I leave my defence to my counsel.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner called seven witnesses, who gave him a good character).</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17810222-30-verdict149" type="verdictDescription">
